body:
Yes, 

```
ldd /usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/tensorflow/python/_pywrap_tensorflow.so
```

shows the dependency. I don't know that we have a build for `7.5`, so at this point I'd recommend building from source.

@gunan for potential additional insights.
